headline: Bank regulator gives BlackRock new deadline on bank stakes, Bloomberg reports
summary: The Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation gave a fresh deadline of Feb. 10 to BlackRock to resolve an issue regarding oversight into the firm's stock in banks, Bloomberg News reported on Sunday,...
